# GitHub Copilot Content Exclusion

Files and directories listed here will NEVER be sent to the Copilot model.
This is the definitive defense against leaking sensitive data via Copilot.

## Environment files with secrets

.env
.env.\*
!.env.example

## Cloud/Service credentials

_credentials_.json
_service-account_.json
_.pem
_.key

## Dependencies (excluded to save tokens — hundreds of thousands of lines)

node_modules/

## Build artifacts

dist/
build/
.next/
out/

## Coverage reports

coverage/

## Generated files

backend/src/generated/
